text: Antoninho is a nickname. Notable people with this name include the following people. *Antoninho, (1921 – 1973), Brazilian footballer born as Antônio Fernandes *Antoninho (footballer) (born 1939), Brazilian footballer born as Benedicto Antonio Angeli *Antoninho Travadinha, professional name of António Vicente Lopes (d. 1987), Cape Verdean musician ==See also== *Antonino (name)
